            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">Marti Lo</supplied>ucetio <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Iulius B<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ulla fontem et it<supplied reason="lost">er per</supplied> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">possessi</supplied>onem suam ad tem<supplied reason="lost">plum</supplied> <lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> Aresaces publice p<supplied reason="lost">osuerunt</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In zwei Teile zersägtes Fragment wohl eines Brunnens; zwischen VCETIO und L in Z. 1 ein kreisrundes Loch als Wasserauslass.</p>
            </div>
